{"tid":1883141,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"注意！連登有極強影響力","createTime":"2020-02-16T17:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T18:42:03.000Z","uid":189283,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4d94bf1ba32100b3ac55c51374914c33e3cbe699","tid":1883141,"uid":189283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:31:23.000Z","msg":"大家都知口罩短缺咗個幾月啦<br />\n前幾星期開親ig fb都見到班frd日日留言<br />\n<strong>兩盒thx</strong><br />\n本來仲想食花生睇係咪真係買到<br />\n自從比連登仔開大量po笑完後<br />\n依兩星期啲<strong>兩盒thx</strong>消失晒<br />\n本身有留言班frd仲要笑返轉頭<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可想而知連登幾大威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好好運用連登嘅影響力</span></strong><br />\n而家隨便入個po都有五毛蹤影<br />\n連登自6月後出晒名，連我父母同親戚都識<br />\n而家仲有好多上咗年紀嘅人睇連登！<br />\n有武漢肺炎唔等如唔需要文宣！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人人都可以係文宣</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n文宣，有對手有電腦有鍵盤就做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>大量戰線可供加入：<br />\nYouTube<br />\nTwitter<br />\nFacebook<br />\nIg<br />\nOpenRice（食黃店打食評，吸引港豬幫襯）<br />\n仲有得閒send email表揚良心節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">歡迎各巴絲留言補充</span><br />\n係咪好簡單呢，心動不如行動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa6586d330bec55ce1d1571db61f82d0926026b","tid":1883141,"uid":189283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:32:54.000Z","msg":"利申兩盒thx未必係連登笑先<br />\n純粹係個例子話比大家知連登嘅用家好多"},{"pid":"e9146b90b01064f1dd1fdce56dd91faf5069e894","tid":1883141,"uid":11013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:39:34.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"htt